title: I Think He Knows
description:
I Think He Knows is the super bop that doesn't get the praise it deserves! Why is this song overlooked by Swifties? And this could be the sister song to another bop that we know and love! Plus what does it mean now that Taylor is in the driver's seat? We dissect and discuss!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? Let us know!
